Summary:            Non-interactive SSH authentication utility
Name:               sshpass
Version:            1.06
Release:            0%{?dist}
License:            GPLv2
Group:              Development/Tools
URL:                http://sshpass.sourceforge.net

Source0:            http://downloads.sourceforge.net/%{name}/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz

